data:
{{version031}}
{{flavour|Fires a bolt of highly destructive energy. The range of the bolt is decreased by one for every creature it strikes.}}

'''Bolt of Devastation''' is a monster-only spell which fires a bolt of irresistible damaging energy and applies [[vulnerability (status effect)|vulnerability]]. Fortunately, it's a fairly inaccurate spell and can be dodged.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.31]], this spell was named '''Energy Bolt''' and did not apply vulnerability.
*Prior to [[0.20]], this spell could destroy walls.

[[Category:Monster spells]]
